1. *Dobrim* danom ću početi svoj dan. (I will start my day with a good day.)
2. Ja sam se već *dobrim* delom oporavio. (I have already recovered with a good deed.)
3. Ona ima *dobrim* ocenama iz škole. (She has good grades from school.)
4. Oni su odgovorni za *dobrim* rezultatima. (They are responsible for good results.)
5. Čestitamo joj na *dobrim* potezima. (We congratulate her on good moves.)
6. Mi smo obezbedili *dobrim* uslovima. (We secured good conditions.)
7. Ona voli da pomaže *dobrim* delima. (She likes to help with good deeds.)
8. *Dobrim* zdravljem smo se oduševili. (We were delighted with good health.)